## 5. 🔗 ERD (Entity Relationship Diagram)

```
Users
  │
  ├── UserRoles ─── Roles
  │
  └── ColumnPermissions


Customers
   │
   ├── CustomerQueues ─── Queues
   │
   ├── DuplicateFlags
   │
   └── CustomerVersions


AuditLogs (log tất cả bảng)
```

---

## 6. 🔄 Data Flow

### 6.1 Update dữ liệu

```
User edit cell
   ↓
API gọi update
   ↓
DB update
   ↓
Audit log
   ↓
Realtime push
```

---

### 6.2 Queue Flow

```
Checkbox click
   ↓
Insert/Delete CustomerQueues
```

---

### 6.3 End of Day Flow

```
00:00 Job
   ↓
Find pending customers
   ↓
Move to next day
```

---

